The RPers site I made is back up and at 100% with some new additions, 
in profiles and sections of the site.  Check it out at it's new 
location: http://lordfirestarter.tripod.com/    



The IGL deadline for entries is technically over as of yesterday, but 
until I finish setting up the matches I will accept new entries.  
Feel free to send them to me privately.  I know some people are gone, 
such as Rdahl, and I will accept late entries from him and anyone 
else, even if the matches have already begun.  Below is a list of 
people currently entered into the IGL.  If there is a mistake, such 
as a name missing or a name that's not supposed to be there, e-mail 
me.  Or just reply to this post.
